# AI Coding Agent Discord Bot Template

This file contains the template for your environment variables. 
To host this on another platform:
1. Create a file named `.env` in the root directory.
2. Copy the contents below into that file.
3. Fill in your own values for the API keys.

```env
# Discord Configuration
DISCORD_TOKEN=MTQ4NTIyMTk3ODkwNTI0Nzc0NQ.G04qh4.Kl1fKClUIokyCmVhBd9oSi9pvkK9nQujZiA6vg

# AI Configuration (OpenAI/Anthropic/Gemini)
# These are required if you are hosting outside of Replit.
# If you use Replit AI Integrations, these are handled automatically.
AI_INTEGRATIONS_OPENAI_BASE_URL=
AI_INTEGRATIONS_OPENAI_API_KEY=
AI_INTEGRATIONS_ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=
AI_INTEGRATIONS_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
AI_INTEGRATIONS_GEMINI_BASE_URL=
AI_INTEGRATIONS_GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Backup AI Configuration (Groq)
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here
```
